title: SIP-06 Add DEGO-ETH and DEGO-SAKE to SakeSwap Fram V2
body:
We propose to add DEGO-ETH and DEGO-SAKE pools to SakeSwap Fram V2. In the meanwhile, DEGO-ETH and DEGO-SAKE trading pairs will be available on SakeSwap Exchange. 

DEGO project is very popular in the NFT community. To attract more SAKE holders and DEGO holders to get involved, related votes will be proceed on SakeSwap Discord community and Snapshot.  Snapshot vote decides whether to add DEGO-ETH and DEGO-SAKE. And the vote on Discord decides the weight of the farming pools. 

Welcome to SakeSwap Discord community: https://discord.gg/uYFVyNX
 
The vote is:
- YES. I support this.
- NO. I don’t.

If there are more positive votes than negative ones, the proposal will be implemented. 

================================================
关于上线DEGO-SAKE交易对的提议：
现在提议增加DEGO-ETH，DEGO-SAKE 流动性池进入sakeswap Farm V2。 DEGO-ETH，DEGO-SAKE交易对会添加至Sakeswap Exchange。DEGO是在NFT社区中非常受欢迎的项目，为了能够吸引SAKE持有者和DEGO持有者支持本次投票，本次投票会在snapshot和discord社区同步投票。snapshot决定是否加入farming白名单，discord社区投票决定farming pool权重比例。 欢迎SAKE持有者和DEGO持有者进行投票。
SakeSwap Discord：https://discord.gg/uYFVyNX
投票通过后，此决议将会被执行。
